pageProduct.name: Aussie Bodies Keto Wafer Cookie & Cream 35g
pageProduct.description:
General Information

FUELLED BY FATS
WITH PROTEIN
NO ADDED SUGAR
KETO CERTIFIED (with logo)
No artificial colours, flavours or preservative

Aussie Bodies Pro-active Nutrition, helps you shape your body from the inside out.
Our KETO nutrition products make sticking to a KETO diet easy. Our products have been formulated witin the KETO guidelines. They have a 70:20:10 calorie ratio split from Fats:Protein:Carbs, so you don't have to do the math. Since 1991

Product Claims: FUELED BY FATS, WITH PROTEIN, NO ADDED SUGAR, KETO CERTIFIED, No artificial colours, flavours or preservatives

Size: 35g

Flavour: Cookies & Cream Wafer

Serving Size: 35g

Servings Per Pack: 1

KEY FEATURES

• Proactive Nutrition
• Great Tasting
• Guilt-Free Indulgence

Ingredients

INGREDIENTS: Protein Milk Chocolate (30%) (Cocoa Butter, Milk Solids, Sweeteners (Erythirtol, Monk Fruit Extract, Steviol Glycosides), Soy Protein Isolate, Cocoa Mass, Prebiotic Fibre (Chicory Root Fibre), Emulsifier (Soy Lecithin), Natural Flavour), Non-hydrogenated Vegetable Fat and Oil [Contains Emulsifier (471), Antioxidants (319, 307b)], Whey Protein Concentrate (Milk), Wheat Flour, Sweetener (Erythritol), Prebiotic Fibre (Chicory Root Fibre), Cocoa Soy Nuggets (Soy Protein Isolate, Cocoa Powder), Emulsifier (Soy Lecithin), Wheat Starch, Cocoa Powder, Natural Flavours, Salt, Natural Colour (Caramel I), Raising Agent (Sodium Bicarbonate), Vitamin B5.

Contains: Contains: Milk, Soy and Cereals Containing Gluten (Wheat).
May Contain: Cereals Containing Gluten (Oats), Peanuts, Tree Nuts (Hazelnuts, Almonds) and Sesame Seeds.

Allergen Contains: Milk| Soy| Wheat| Cereals Containing Gluten

Allergen May Be Present: Almonds| Hazelnuts| Oats| Peanuts| Sesame Seeds| Tree Nuts| Cereals Containing Gluten

Directions

Great as a delicious snack or mini meal on the go, keeping you on track with your KETO diet.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store in a cool, dry place, below 30°C.
